--[[
== Zecred ==

Enemies
explode,
miners give
bonuses.

--]]

dofile("scripts/utils/binder.lua")

-- functions
local initialize
local drawListener
local setupListener
local disposeListener
local updateZecredUi

-- global variables
local roadTiles = {}

local gvProjSpeed
local gvAttackSpeed
local gvUpgradeLevel
local coinsAdded = 0
local healthAdded = 0

local Label -- binding to gdx's Label class, becomes nil after deserialization (Label is not in registry)
local uiLayer -- becomes nil after deserialization (UiLayer is not in registry)
local statsLabel -- becomes nil after deserialization (Label is not in registry)

local uiVars = {
    _noSyncCheck = true,
    uiNeedsUpdate = false
}

local addEnemy = function(enemyType, speed, health, killScore, killBounty, killExp, tileX, tileY, sideShift)
    local creep = managers.EnemyManager:getFactory(enemyType):create()
    creep:setSpeed(speed)
    creep.maxHealth = health;
    creep:setHealth(health);
    creep.killScore = killScore;
    creep.bounty = killBounty;
    creep:setKillExp(killExp);

    local tile = SP.map:getMap():getTile(tileX, tileY)
    SP.enemy:addEnemy(creep, tile, sideShift)
end

-- System listeners --------------------------------------------------------------------------------

local enemySystemListener = luajava.createProxy(GNS .. "systems.EnemySystem$EnemySystemListener", {
    enemyDie = function(enemy, tower, damageType, fromAbility)
        local explosion = managers.ExplosionManager:getFactory(enums.ExplosionType.GENERIC):obtain();

        local enemyFactory = managers.EnemyManager:getFactory(enemy.type)
        explosion:setup(tower, enemy:getPosition().x, enemy:getPosition().y, enemy.maxHealth * 0.05, 1.25, 0, enemyFactory:getColor())
        SP.explosion:register(explosion)
        explosion:explode()
    end,

    enemyReachedTarget = function(enemy)

    end,

    affectsGameState = function() return true end,
    getConstantId = function() return 1000901 end
})

local mapSystemListener = luajava.createProxy(GNS .. "systems.MapSystem$MapSystemListener", {
    enemySpawnedOnMap = function(enemy)
        if enemy.killScore == 0 then return nil end

        local road = roadTiles[utils.syncRandInt(#roadTiles) + 1]
        addEnemy(
                enemy.type,
                enemy:getSpeed(),
                enemy.maxHealth,
                0,
                0,
                enemy:getKillExp(),
                road:getX(),
                road:getY(),
                -1)
    end,

    affectsGameState = function() return true end,
    getConstantId = function() return 1000902 end
})

local minerSystemListener = luajava.createProxy(GNS .. "systems.MinerSystem$MinerSystemListener", {
    minerResourcesChanged = function(miner, resourceType, delta, mined)
        if mined then
            SP.gameState:removeResources(resourceType, delta);

            if resourceType == enums.ResourceType.SCALAR then
                SP.gameState:addMoney(5 * delta, true)
                coinsAdded = coinsAdded + 5 * delta
            elseif resourceType == enums.ResourceType.VECTOR then
                gvProjSpeed.value = gvProjSpeed.value + 1
            elseif resourceType == enums.ResourceType.MATRIX then
                gvAttackSpeed.value = gvAttackSpeed.value + 1
            elseif resourceType == enums.ResourceType.TENSOR then
                SP.gameState:addHealth(delta)
                healthAdded = healthAdded + delta
            elseif resourceType == enums.ResourceType.INFIAR then
                if gvUpgradeLevel.value < 9 then
                    gvUpgradeLevel.value = gvUpgradeLevel.value + 1
                end
            end

            SP.gameValue:recalculate()

            uiVars.uiNeedsUpdate = true
        end
    end,

    affectsGameState = function() return true end,
    getConstantId = function() return 1000903 end
})

-- Functions and script system listeners -----------------------------------------------------------

updateZecredUi = function()
    uiVars.uiNeedsUpdate = false

    if SP._graphics == nil then return end -- No graphics - skipping

    --  Example - restore bindings and UI in a runtime:
    --
    --    if uiLayer == nil then
    --        -- uiLayer was not created or has being nilled after deserialization - recreating UI
    --        uiLayer = managers.UiManager:addLayer(MainUiLayer.SCREEN, 9009, "zecred stats")
    --
    --        if Label == nil then
    --            Label = luajava.bindClass(GDXNS .. "scenes.scene2d.ui.Label")
    --        end
    --
    --        statsLabel = luajava.new(Label, "", managers.AssetManager:getLabelStyle(CFG.FONT_SIZE_SMALL))
    --        statsLabel:setAlignment(0)
    --        uiLayer:getTable():add(statsLabel):expandY():bottom():padBottom(16)
    --    end

    -- updating ui
    statsLabel:setText("Projectile speed: " .. gvProjSpeed.value .. "\n"
            .. "Attack speed: " .. gvAttackSpeed.value .. "\n"
            .. "Upgrade level: " .. gvUpgradeLevel.value .. "\n"
            .. "Coins: " .. coinsAdded .. "\n"
            .. "Health: " .. healthAdded)
end

drawListener = function(batch, deltaTime)
    if uiVars.uiNeedsUpdate or uiLayer == nil then
        updateZecredUi()
    end
end

-- Listens for state restoration (state being deserialized)
-- It is a proper place to restore bindings and recreate UI
-- You can also do that during runtime by checking whether the variable became empty with == nil
initialize = function()
    if SP._graphics ~= nil then
        Label = luajava.bindClass(GDXNS .. "scenes.scene2d.ui.Label")

        uiLayer = managers.UiManager:addLayer(bind("managers.UiManager$MainUiLayer").SCREEN, 9009, "zecred stats")
        statsLabel = luajava.new(Label, "", managers.AssetManager:getLabelStyle(CFG.FONT_SIZE_SMALL))
        statsLabel:setAlignment(0)
        uiLayer:getTable():add(statsLabel):expandY():bottom():padBottom(16 + math.random() * 10)

        log("UI recreated")
    end
    uiVars.uiNeedsUpdate = true

    -- TODO restore class bindings / recreate UI and other stuff which is not being serialized
    log("State restored")
end

setupListener = function()
    local tiles = SP.map:getMap().tilesArray
    for i = 1, tiles.size do
        local tile = tiles.items[i]
        if tile.type == enums.TileType.ROAD then
            table.insert(roadTiles, tile)
        end
    end
    log((#roadTiles) .. " road tiles found")

    gvProjSpeed = luajava.newInstance(GNS .. "GameValueConfig", enums.GameValueType.TOWERS_PROJECTILE_SPEED, 0, false, false)
    SP.map:getMap().targetTile:addGameValue(gvProjSpeed)
    gvAttackSpeed = luajava.newInstance(GNS .. "GameValueConfig", enums.GameValueType.TOWERS_ATTACK_SPEED, 0, false, false)
    SP.map:getMap().targetTile:addGameValue(gvAttackSpeed)
    gvUpgradeLevel = luajava.newInstance(GNS .. "GameValueConfig", enums.GameValueType.TOWERS_MAX_UPGRADE_LEVEL, 0, false, false)
    SP.map:getMap().targetTile:addGameValue(gvUpgradeLevel)

    addEventHandler("SystemDispose", disposeListener)

    SP.enemy.listeners:add(enemySystemListener)
    SP.map.listeners:add(mapSystemListener)
    SP.miner.listeners:add(minerSystemListener)

    initialize()
end

disposeListener = function()
    removeEventHandler("SystemDraw", drawListener)
    removeEventHandler("SystemPostSetup", setupListener)
    removeEventHandler("SystemDispose", disposeListener)
    removeEventHandler("StateRestored", initialize)

    SP.enemy.listeners:remove(enemySystemListener)
    SP.map.listeners:remove(mapSystemListener)
    SP.miner.listeners:remove(minerSystemListener)

    if uiLayer ~= nil then
        managers.UiManager:removeLayer(uiLayer)
        uiLayer = nil
    end
end

addEventHandler("StateRestored", initialize)
addEventHandler("SystemPostSetup", setupListener)
addEventHandler("SystemDraw", drawListener)
